entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have met with Madison Silane about her missing husband.
entries.journal_entry_description: You were able to complete your mission for CorSec. It appears all is well. It looks like things are back to normal...or are they?
entries.task01_comm_message_text: I understand you helped my friend Angela find her missing husband. Please I need your help. I am on Corellia, in the city of Tyrena. Please come see me personally.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: A friend of Angela's is trying to contact you.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: A friend of Angela's has contacted you after helping Angela. It looks like Angela's friend Madison needs help as well. A hero's work is never done.
